()).startsWith(\"junit\");\n        } finally {\n            temporaryFolder.delete();\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void createsRootFolderInConfiguredParentDirectory() throws IOException {\n        Path parent = Files.createTempDirectory(\"junit-parent\");\n        TemporaryFolder temporaryFolder = new TemporaryFolder(parent.toFile());\n\n        try {\n            temporaryFolder.create();\n            File root = temporaryFolder.getRoot();\n\n            assertThat(root).isDirectory();\n            assertThat(root.getName()).startsWith(\"junit\");\n            assertThat(root.getParentFile().getCanonicalFile()).isEqualTo(parent.toFile().getCanonicalFile());\n        } finally {\n            temporaryFolder.delete();\n            Files.deleteIfExists(parent);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 514, "output": 870, "cacheRead": 43520, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 44904, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780808919031, "responseId": "resp_02a1498fde37fe72016a24fcd77a1881908c6b3ec5bb6070bd"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_7gbdIfE5YcsIPtRu0tbOCk60|fc_02a1498fde37fe72016a24fce2be2c8190b0cb24bf2639c87d", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1603 bytes to tests/src/junit/junit/3.7/src/test/java/junit_junit/TemporaryFolderTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780808933980}]}
